{"comments":"Online Selection State\n\nThis module defines the state maintained by each agent for online\nsubmodular optimization. The state tracks marginal gain estimates\nand enables efficient lazy greedy selection.\n\n## Memory Budget\n\nFrom systems architect analysis, each agent maintains ~2.5KB:\n- Gradients for active regions (56 max × 20 bytes ≈ 1.1KB)\n- Partition assignment (~1KB)\n- Overhead (~400 bytes)\n\nThis scales to billion-agent deployment without memory pressure.\n\n## State Update Flow\n\n```\nEpoch N:\n  1. Read previous frame results\n  2. Update gradient estimates (EMA smoothing)\n  3. Run greedy selection using cached gradients\n  4. Dispatch render commands\n  5. Wait for results\n  6. Observe actual utility → update for Epoch N+1\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["gradients",{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Map","Internal"],"Map"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Core"],"RegionId"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Selection","State"],"MarginalEstimate"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["ema",{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Map","Internal"],"Map"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Core"],"RegionId"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Selection","State"],"EMAState"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["epoch",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Core"],"EpochId"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[